{"expireTime":9007200818315815000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-b576cf2f57f3e7dc03c5a1dcc1c40089-gatsby-remark-katexgatsby-remark-prismjs-","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"读书时看到记述古罗马人何时开始有理发师，及何时少有人蓄须，突然对我国古人的胡子问题颇感兴趣。查询之后，找到了沈从文先生的一篇《从文物来谈古人胡子问题》，引经据典，也很有趣，所以在此整理一下。","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":96,"offset":96},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":96,"offset":96},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"西汉及之前","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":5,"offset":102},"end":{"line":4,"column":10,"offset":107},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":98},"end":{"line":4,"column":10,"offset":107},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"从商代遗留下来的各种材质的人头雕件，铸件可以看出，当时的人留胡子的，不留胡子都有，这一点和身份地位无关，因为安阳出土的一个贵族雕刻，一个奴隶雕刻都是光光的下巴。而到了春秋战国，出土资料更多，可以从中看出有部分地区有着特定的爱好流行风气。但同样有画作上的人物既有留胡子的，也有不留的。西汉时期的壁画已经出现了明显的用须髯表示英武，而文臣只留一点的特点了。不过这个时期仍存在着一点不留的人。","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":109},"end":{"line":6,"column":194,"offset":302},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":109},"end":{"line":6,"column":194,"offset":302},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"总结来说，","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":8,"column":6,"offset":309},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":304},"end":{"line":8,"column":6,"offset":309},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"即此可知，关于古代由商到汉，胡子去留实大有伸缩余地，有些自觉自愿意味，并不受法律或一定社会习惯限制。","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":2,"offset":312},"end":{"line":10,"column":52,"offset":362},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":2,"offset":312},"end":{"line":10,"column":52,"offset":362},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":311},"end":{"line":10,"column":52,"offset":362},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"汉魏时期","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":5,"offset":368},"end":{"line":12,"column":9,"offset":372},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":364},"end":{"line":12,"column":9,"offset":372},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"汉魏时期有着更丰富的文物展示劳动人民形象，各行各业极少见留胡子的。上流阶层也很少有留大把胡子，做多也就是乐府诗提及的“为人洁白晰，颇有须”，也就是一小撮儿。很难认为统计阶级以茂盛的胡须作为审美标准。","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":374},"end":{"line":14,"column":100,"offset":473},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":374},"end":{"line":14,"column":100,"offset":473},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"不仅如此，魏晋以来很长的时间，胡子都不受重视，可能与宦官得宠有关。美须髯甚至已经成为了歌舞喜剧中的笑料。汉初，张良的貌如妇人，和陈平的美如冠玉，虽未见得是称赞，但看不出讥讽。魏晋以来有文献记载有人对胡子极其呵护，但和美男子关系不多。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":475},"end":{"line":16,"column":117,"offset":591},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":475},"end":{"line":16,"column":117,"offset":591},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"事实正相反，魏晋之际社会日趋病态，所以“何郎敷粉，荀令熏香”，以男子而具妇女柔媚姿态竟为一时美的标准。史传叙述到这一点时，尽管具有深刻讥讽，可是这种对于男性的病态审美观，在社会中却继续发生显明影响，直到南北朝末期。这从《世说》记载潘安上街，妇女掷果满车，左思入市，群妪大掷石头故事及其他叙述可知。","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":595},"end":{"line":18,"column":151,"offset":743},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":595},"end":{"line":18,"column":151,"offset":743},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":593},"end":{"line":18,"column":151,"offset":743},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南北朝时期","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":5,"offset":749},"end":{"line":20,"column":10,"offset":754},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":745},"end":{"line":20,"column":10,"offset":754},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"元魏拓跋氏统一北方之后，胡子本应大受重视，但存留下来的人物形象中，嘴边总是光光的。","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":756},"end":{"line":22,"column":42,"offset":797},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":1,"offset":756},"end":{"line":22,"column":42,"offset":797},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"可知身属北方胡族，即到中年，也居多并不曾留胡子。传世《北齐校书图》作魏收等人画像，也有好几位没有胡子，画中胡子最多还是那位马夫。","position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":3,"offset":801},"end":{"line":24,"column":67,"offset":865},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":3,"offset":801},"end":{"line":24,"column":67,"offset":865},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":24,"column":1,"offset":799},"end":{"line":24,"column":67,"offset":865},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"唐","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":4,"offset":870},"end":{"line":26,"column":5,"offset":871},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":1,"offset":867},"end":{"line":26,"column":5,"offset":871},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"从敦煌壁画中描绘贞观时的大臣形象中，既有不留胡子的，也有相貌英挺但胡子垂下的。","position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":873},"end":{"line":28,"column":40,"offset":912},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":28,"column":1,"offset":873},"end":{"line":28,"column":40,"offset":912},"indent":[]}},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"总之，除太宗天生虬髯为既定事实，画尉迟敬德作毛胡子以示英武外，始终还看不出胡子多是美男子特点之一的情形。一般毛胡子倒多依旧表现到身份较低的人物身上","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":2,"offset":915},"end":{"line":30,"column":75,"offset":988},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":2,"offset":915},"end":{"line":30,"column":75,"offset":988},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":1,"offset":914},"end":{"line":30,"column":75,"offset":988},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"中唐之后仍是这样。","position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":990},"end":{"line":32,"column":10,"offset":999},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":32,"column":1,"offset":990},"end":{"line":32,"column":10,"offset":999},"indent":[]}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"参考文献","position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":5,"offset":1005},"end":{"line":34,"column":9,"offset":1009},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":34,"column":1,"offset":1001},"end":{"line":34,"column":9,"offset":1009},"indent":[]}},{"type":"list","ordered":true,"start":1,"spread":false,"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"沈从文，《从文物来谈古人的胡子问题》","position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":4,"offset":1014},"end":{"line":36,"column":22,"offset":1032},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":4,"offset":1014},"end":{"line":36,"column":22,"offset":1032},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":1011},"end":{"line":36,"column":22,"offset":1032},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":36,"column":1,"offset":1011},"end":{"line":36,"column":22,"offset":1032},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":36,"column":22,"offset":1032}}}}